    s "Up the ladder, now!"

# OutsideOfBagrad_ab7aaef6 (line 38517)
translate ru OutsideOfBagrad_ab7aaef6:
    # "Hungry for battle, she saw the first of her soldiers begin scaling the ladder."
    ""

# OutsideOfBagrad_a797a059 (line 38518)
translate ru OutsideOfBagrad_a797a059:
    # "Not long after, Sarah felt her own urge overtake her, leaping onto the ladder and beginning to climb."
    ""

# OutsideOfBagrad_0c88af0b (line 38519)
translate ru OutsideOfBagrad_0c88af0b:
    # "Don't look down, she thought to herself at the halfway point."
    ""

# OutsideOfBagrad_e08b73c5 (line 38520)
translate ru OutsideOfBagrad_e08b73c5:
    # "Eager for battle, but scared of heights, she joked to herself."
    ""

# OutsideOfBagrad_87951d5c (line 38521)
translate ru OutsideOfBagrad_87951d5c:
    # "Suddenly an ear piercing scream rang out and Sarah saw a shadow shift past the ladder."
    ""

# OutsideOfBagrad_00f0834c (line 38522)
translate ru OutsideOfBagrad_00f0834c:
    # "Looking down, against her own instincts, she saw that the first man up the ladder was now falling down, screaming as he did."
    ""

# OutsideOfBagrad_5c044ac7 (line 38523)
translate ru OutsideOfBagrad_5c044ac7:
    # "Smoke was rising from his face. But Sarah realized, there wasn't much of a face there, only a pitch black goo that bubbled."
    ""

# OutsideOfBagrad_e3b168c9 (line 38524)
translate ru OutsideOfBagrad_e3b168c9:
    # "Boiling oil, she realized. They were throwing burning oil down at them."
    ""

# OutsideOfBagrad_02bcad5e (line 38525)
translate ru OutsideOfBagrad_02bcad5e:
    # "Hesitation now meant death."
    ""

# OutsideOfBagrad_bf1dd999 (line 38526)
translate ru OutsideOfBagrad_bf1dd999:
